  repo register <owner_name>           Register a repository owner
  repo auth <owner_name>               Authenticate as a repository owner
  pkg add <url>                        Add a compiled package to the current project
  pkg info <package>                   Show information about a compiled package
  pkg verify                           Verify packages declared by project.json
  pkg publish <owner_name> <package>   Publish a signed package project
  pkg doc <name-or-path> [--out file]  Render HTML docs from a compiled package
  doc [--out file] [location]          Render HTML docs from package or file source
  fmt [--check] [--indent N] [location] Format project source (indentation and capitalization)
  build [--sign owner] [-ast|-ir|-br|-nir|-nplan|-nobj|-ncode|-mir]... [-target os-arch] [-app] [location] Validate and build an MFBASIC project (output flags combine; each requested artifact is written in one pass)
